{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1778430577620,"sessionID":"ses_1ed4705d6ffeksNKE6jb7AhPQa","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_op9nyebsx257J2hUW9BBiWxz","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/__w/eval-ont-agent-go/eval-ont-agent-go/__issue_context__.json","offset":1,"limit":2000},"output":"<path>/__w/eval-ont-agent-go/eval-ont-agent-go/__issue_context__.json</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: {\n2:   \"body\": \"Please provide as much information as you can:\\n\\n* **GO term ID and Label**\\n\\nGO:0140057    vacuole-mitochondria membrane tethering\\n\\n\\n* **Reason for deprecation** Put an x in the appropriate box: \\n\\n - [x]  The reason for obsoletion is that this term was added in error.\\n\\n\\n* **Are there annotations to this term?**\\n- How many EXP: 1 PomBase removed\\n\\n* **Are there mappings and cross references to this term? (InterPro, Keywords; check QuickGO cross-references section)**\\n\\n* **Is this term in a subset? (check the AmiGO page for that term)**\\n\\n* **Any other information**\\n\\n\\n----\\nChecklist for ontology editor\\n\\n***Check term usage and metadata in Protégé***\\n- [ ] check term usage in the ontology \\n- [ ] check internal mappings: RHEA, EC, MetaCyc\\n- [ ] check subset usage\\n- [ ] check taxon constraints \\n\\n***Check annotations***\\n- [ ] create Annotation Review spreadsheet \\n- * Annotation Review template: https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1izV3q1jnq_Ybg5MJ53O_b5BCTkGtjl_Fi-cOg3-7eBE/edit#gid=0\\n- * Instructions: https://wiki.geneontology.org/Annotation_Review_Request\\n- [ ] create annotation review ticket: https://github.com/geneontology/go-annotation/issues/new?assignees=&labels=annotation+review&template=annotation-review-for-obsoletion.md&title=Review+annotations+to+%5BINSERT+GO+TERM%5D\\n- [ ] find external mappings (via IEAS), include in obsoletion notice  \\n- [ ] tag curators in Annotation Review ticket. Responsible annotator for each group: https://github.com/geneontology/go-site/blob/master/metadata/group-contacts.csv\\n\\n***Notification***\\n- [ ] create [obsoletion announcement](https://github.com/geneontology/go-announcements/issues/new?assignees=&labels=obsoletion&template=obsoletion-notice.md&title=Obsoletion+notice%3A+%5BGO+ID%3A+term+label%5D)\\n- [ ] announce to GO friends (go-friends@mailman.stanford.edu)\\n- [ ] paste the text in the ontology ticket\\n\",\n3:   \"comments\": [\n4:     {\n5:       \"id\": \"IC_kwDOAkAHws8AAAABAFvrRg\",\n6:       \"author\": {\n7:         \"login\": \"raymond91125\"\n8:       },\n9:       \"authorAssociation\": \"MEMBER\",\n10:       \"body\": \"@dragon-ai-agent please obsolete GO:0140057 vacuole-mitochondria membrane tethering.\",\n11:       \"createdAt\": \"2026-04-23T01:00:54Z\",\n12:       \"includesCreatedEdit\": false,\n13:       \"isMinimized\": false,\n14:       \"minimizedReason\": \"\",\n15:       \"reactionGroups\": [\n16:         {\n17:           \"content\": \"EYES\",\n18:           \"users\": {\n19:             \"totalCount\": 1\n20:           }\n21:         }\n22:       ],\n23:       \"url\": \"https://github.com/geneontology/go-ontology/issues/31876#issuecomment-4300991302\",\n24:       \"viewerDidAuthor\": false\n25:     },\n26:     {\n27:       \"id\": \"IC_kwDOAkAHws8AAAABAFvwqg\",\n28:       \"author\": {\n29:         \"login\": \"dragon-ai-agent\"\n30:       },\n31:       \"authorAssociation\": \"MEMBER\",\n32:       \"body\": \"🤖 Working on it...\\n\\nFollow along: [View workflow run](https://github.com/geneontology/go-ontology/actions/runs/24810816975)\\n\\n*— @dragon-ai-agent*\",\n33:       \"createdAt\": \"2026-04-23T01:01:15Z\",\n34:       \"includesCreatedEdit\": false,\n35:       \"isMinimized\": false,\n36:       \"minimizedReason\": \"\",\n37:       \"reactionGroups\": [],\n38:       \"url\": \"https://github.com/geneontology/go-ontology/issues/31876#issuecomment-4300992682\",\n39:       \"viewerDidAuthor\": true\n40:     }\n41:   ],\n42:   \"title\": \"O